name: Metamorphosis
description: The metamorphosis has started. ‘Metamorphosis’ represents the similarities between the lemon and a human being. The human being slowly becomes one with the lemon and embodies the characteristics. ‘Metamorphosis’ is the first nft in the second part of the lemon collection. The second part of the lemon collection tells the rest of the story in 6 illustrations. This part is about becoming and sharing the lemon. Digital artwork made in 2021 by Camila Trapasso (camamblo).
